#
msgid ""
msgstr ""
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:107
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_MIXED_SIGNAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears that the enemy ship is sending out a distress signal to a nearby "
"fleet! Though, since both fleets are fighting each other, letting this "
"signal go through would mean the enemy would also be targeted."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:109
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_MIXED_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Signal Diluter) Jam their signal."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:111
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_MIXED_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"When no ASB activates, you assume that it's a good sign that your augment "
"has functioned properly, and you continue to fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:115
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_MIXED_SIGNAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:124
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_HOSTILE_SIGNAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears the enemy ship is sending out a distress signal to a nearby "
"fleet! Brace for impact!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:126
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_HOSTILE_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Signal Diluter) Jam their signal."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:128
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_HOSTILE_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"When no ASB activates, you assume that it's a good sign that your augment "
"has functioned properly, and you continue to fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:132
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_HOSTILE_SIGNAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:141
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_ALLY_SIGNAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears that an ally ship is sending out a distress signal to a nearby "
"fleet! You could intercept it if you don't need the backup."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:143
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_ALLY_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Signal Diluter) Jam their signal."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:145
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_ALLY_SIGNAL\"]/choice[@req=\"PDS_DISABLE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"When no ASB activates, you assume that it's a good sign that your augment "
"has functioned properly, and you continue to fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:149
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_ALLY_SIGNAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:179
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "The location of the Federation Research HQ."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:180
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Nothing left of interest."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:181
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip"
msgstr "An unvisited location."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:183
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at the Federation Research Headquarters, or at least what's left "
"of it, though it seems to be in surprisingly good condition given it was "
"atacked by a whole fleet not too long ago. A small Federation scout scans "
"your ship just to make sure you are not a threat before flying away towards "
"the base."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:186
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Follow the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:188
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The scout leads you to the landing pad of the facility; the journey is quick and uneventful, with the radio eeriely quiet. After landing your ship and disembarking, you are greeted by worn Defender Engi with a missing arm and a cracked visor, flanked by 2 Federation elite soldiers. \n"
"\n"
"\"Federation Renegade, welcome. I am: Lead Scientist HS-98A. Specialization = Flagship model ships. I was in charge of: Project Retribution.\" The Engi explains, despite the fact that their broken voice synthesizer is struggling to keep up with their thoughts.\n"
"        \n"
"\"Project was = Near completion when Rebel forces attacked. They stole: Prototype Flagship made for the Federation. We were forced to: Teach them how to pilot it or else we would have been all killed.\" The Engi's tone seems emotionless as usual, but you could imagine a tinge of regret in their synthetic voice."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:194
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Let me guess, you want us to retrieve the ship?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:196
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi nods robotically. \"That is what this unit hopes, yes. If the flagship were to be adapted by the Rebellion, then it's this unit's fear that it may doom our reality.\" The Engi speaks in a tone that almost sounds grim.\n"
"                                        \n"
"\"I know Renegades do not work for price = free. Thus I purpose a: mutually beneficial arrengement. You clear the flagship of rebels while keeping the ship = intact and you may keep the ship's: blueprints. How does this offer sound?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:200
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "You can count us in!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:202
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi nods. \"Very well. Luckily we can track: the Flagship. We will add "
"a marker to: your map.\" HS-98A transmits the coordinates to your ship "
"before shutting off for a moment, rebooting a few seconds later."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:205
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Are you okay?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:207
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi nods sluggishly. \"My form = Irrevelent in the face of the "
"Rebellion.\" Suddenly, the Engi stops for a moment before they turn back to "
"you hastily. \"There seems to be another issue, Renegade. The Coalition has "
"also sent a flagship of their own. It seems to be: Attacking Rebels for now."
" However, once the Rebels are dealt with, they will surely turn their guns "
"towards: The Federation. Would you deal with this threat as well? This unit "
"is sure that you might also receive: compensation for it.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:209
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Sure."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:211
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi nods before their body slowly shuts down, though this time they "
"don't turn themselves back on. The guards thank you for your help and let "
"you be on your way."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:216
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We have enough on our plate. We must pass."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:218
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi nods slowly shutting off, this time for good. The soldiers guide "
"you back to your ship and you set off with your target in mind."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:220
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:224
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:234
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "That sounds too dangerous, we can't risk it."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:236
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "The Engi nods before allowing you and your crew to leave."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:238
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:242
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:252
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "This is suspicious, avoid the ship and prepare to jump away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:254
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Knowing how dangerous this sector is, trusting any random ship, even "
"Federation ones, is a risk too great to take right now."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:256
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:260
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:270
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "Location of the stolen Federation Flagship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:271
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Nothing left of interest."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:281
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You've tracked down the location of the stolen Federation flagship; it seems"
" to be in the middle of a rebel hanger. Security is surprisingly light as "
"well, though you doubt it will stay like that for long."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:286
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Flagship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:288
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You charge fowards, forcing the ship to engage you. It seems the rebels "
"didn't have enough time to fully paint over the ship in Rebel colors. Still,"
" it seems its weapons are fully online. You are suddenly hailed by the "
"flagship. On your screen appears a rebel wearing an aviator helmet covering "
"their bright red hair. \"So you are the Renegade the Federation sent to stop"
" us, huh? That's very cute. Our cause is too great to be stopped by a brown-"
"nosed Federation dog like you. Be ready to feel the wrath of the Rebellion! "
"For I, Victor, will strike you down!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:291
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:295
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Vance Prime) \"Halt, soldier! I order you to evacuate the flagship and "
"deliver it back to the Federation's HQ in one piece!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:297
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Victor blinks before their face contorts in pure anger. \"You traitorous "
"rat! You left us to tail back to the crumbling hive of filth that is the "
"Federation! You are no Rebel! You are a disgrace, a disease! One I will "
"gladly eliminate!\" Victor turns off the feed and attacks, leaving Vance "
"fuming."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:299
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:307
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:309
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Attacking this ship is akin to throwing a stone at a hornet's nest. You "
"decide you like living and so you quickly leave before being detected."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:311
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:315
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:323
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_DEADCREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As the last remaining rebels fall, you know you don't have any seconds to "
"waste. The rebels have certainly asked for reinforcements before they died, "
"meaning that you need to be quick if you want to get the blueprints."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:326
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_DEADCREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:328
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_DEADCREW\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It takes a minute to find the right schematics, but you manage to get them. "
"It's a shame the project won't be deployed soon, but at least you prevented "
"the rebels from ever using it. You also locate a unique modified gun on your"
" way out. It seems reserved for only the highest-ranking Federation "
"soldiers, but you figure it should be fine to take it."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:332
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_FEDERATION_FLAGSHIP_DEADCREW\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:343
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "Location of the stolen Coalition Flagship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:344
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Nothing left of interest."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:354
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You've tracked down the location of the Coalition flagship, seemingly "
"focused on attacking a small Rebel outpost. There's barely any ships "
"defending it aside from a few technician ships, they won't last long without"
" your help."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:359
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Flagship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:361
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You charge onwards, forcing the flagship to engage you. You receive a transmission from the flagship; on the other end is no less than a rock elder!\n"
"\n"
"\"Ah, the weak and pathetic Federation ship; I've heard a lot about your struggle. You haven't got an idea of what you are signing up for, have you? I'm Rockmore, the Elder in charge of the Inquisition's research, and I'm here to make sure both the Rebels and the Federation are without any technology that might aid them against the Crusade. I will enjoy watching you struggle, little fly.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:366
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:372
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "The rebels can fend for themselves."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:374
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They were the ones that started this mess; this is karma in your book."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:376
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:380
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:388
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_DESTROYED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The massive flagship cracks in half before exploding. While you did save the"
" technicians, the blueprints of the flagship are now lost forever."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:392
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_DESTROYED\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:394
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_DESTROYED\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You are soon hailed by the technician dressed in MV Rebel colors from the outpost. \"Renegade, thank the heavens you arrived! The flagship, it attacked us suddenly! This outpost wasn't meant for combat; it was simply a place to repair our auto-ships. The few ships we had defending us were destroyed in seconds... I can't imagine what would have happened if you hadn't got here.\"\n"
"\n"
"The rebel clears his throat. \"My name is Jon Briggs. I'm the lead technician here, sent by Universe 1 to help train the new generation of technicians. Though, seeing all the carnage the Rebellion did here with my own eyes... I fear I'm not cut out for this job anymore. Would you mind if I joined your crew?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:397
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_DESTROYED\"]/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Jon Briggs"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:403
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_DEADCREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Rockmore puts up a good fight, being the last one to fall; however, even his"
" mighty hammer can't stop you. You quickly locate the control panel and "
"download the blueprints before scrapping the ship. You also find a unique "
"weapon, one much more powerful than the standard variant, problably reserved"
" for only the mightiest of Coalition soldiers."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:408
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_DEADCREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:410
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_DEADCREW\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You are soon hailed by the technician dressed in MV Rebel colors from the outpost. \"Renegade, thank the heavens you arrived! The flagship, it attacked us suddenly! This outpost wasn't meant for combat; it was simply a place to repair our auto-ships. The few ships we had defending us were destroyed in seconds... I can't imagine what would have happened if you hadn't got here.\"\n"
"\n"
"The rebel clears his throat. \"My name is Jon. I'm the lead technician here, sent by Universe 1 to help train the new generation of technicians. Though, seeing all the carnage the Rebellion did here with my own eyes... I fear I'm not cut out for this job anymore. Would you mind if I joined your crew?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:413
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HQ_COALITION_FLAGSHIP_DEADCREW\"]/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Jon Briggs"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:438
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty pirate ship cracks in half, its advanced design clearly reaching its limits. Still, some mechanism in its construction prevents its total destruction, with only half the ship blowing up.\n"
"\n"
"You first scrap the destroyed half; in it, you find the highly advanced weapon Purple Beard used against you, still intact even after such an explosion! The other laser seems to have been badly damaged during the fight, however, to the point where it can no longer be used."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:444
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:449
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Purple Beard was an exceptional opponent, but even he had his limits. The fight is long and painful but eventually the last of his crew falls, leaving the rest of his ship ready for scrapping.\n"
"\n"
"The first thing you attempt to recover is his powerful lasers; however, it seems one of them was damaged badly during the fight and can't be recovered. At least the other one is in perfect condition."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:455
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:472
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you jump into this beacon you are immediately hailed by the only other ship at this beacon... at least, apart from the giant fleet in the background. \"Renegade... So it seems our paths have finally crossed...\" The man on the screen is the legendary corsair Purple Beard, the only unaffiliated  pirate to ever reach such a rank.\n"
"\n"
"\tHis voice is slow and heavy; even though he avoids looking at you in the eyes, you can still feel a tremandous weight behind his own. His apperance reinforces the legends told about him in the less savory places of the multiverse, about an ex-Legionarre Rebel who betrayed his own after becoming disillusioned with the cause. With every faction wanting him dead for his past, the only path he could tread was that of a pirate."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:478
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "So you are the legendary Purple Beard?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:480
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate winces at the name but slowly nods. \"...Yes, I am... Though... I"
" wish I weren't...\" The man glances away. His eyes are visible for just a "
"moment: one, a cybernetic replacement eye, and the other, a glass eye with a"
" scar crossing it vertically. \"And I suppose... you wish to kill me?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:482
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Not really."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:484
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The legend seems taken aback by your admission. \"...you... do not?... Why? "
"I am the number one most wanted criminal in all the Multiverse!\" Once more,"
" you catch a glimpse of his eyes. A mix of shock and perhaps a bit of hope "
"seems to show."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:486
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"We are Renegades; our reputation isn't much better than yours in some parts."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:488
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The man lets out a dry chuckle before coughing violently. Once he recovers, "
"he once again speaks. \"... I see... So... if you do not wish to kill me... "
"what do you want?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:490
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"You don't seem to enjoy being a pirate. Why not join our crew and become a "
"hero?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:492
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Purple Beard freezes for a moment, his eyes now fully visible. A slight tear"
" forms on their corners before it is swiftly removed with his aged sleeves. "
"He smiles slightly as he finally looks at you directly in the eyes. "
"\"...Heh... If you aren't the weirdest Renegade I've ever met... Truth be "
"told... I always wished I could... start over... Very well, Renegade... I "
"accept your offer... However... I can't just leave... A legend like me "
"deserves a good death... Tell you what... you will fight me and my crew... "
"Feel free to be as violent as you wish... make it something worthy of my "
"legend... Once the fight ends, scrap this ship... I have a plan... En "
"garde...\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:496
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:506
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Yes."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:508
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate sighs. \"...Very well... Good luck... Renegade...\" The feed cuts"
" and the pirate's weapons go online."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:511
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:521
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate fleet suddunly stops dead in their tracks as they realize the "
"legend has been defeated. You are soon hailed by a giant rockman outcast "
"inside the pirate fleet. \"You... you killed him... I can barely belive my "
"eyes! Renegade! I don't know if you realize what you have just done, but by "
"killing Purple Beard, you will now take his place in our legends!\" She then"
" hails all other fleet ships. \"Everyone! Stop attacking the Renegade at "
"once! They are now our leader!\" You are suddunly flooded with hails from "
"every pirate ship in the beacon, all singing songs in your honor. It isn't "
"too long before a small pirate shuttle delivers a box of supplies to you. It"
" seems piracy pays off... sometimes."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:527
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD_WIN_PLAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate fleet suddunly stops dead in their tracks as they realize the "
"legend has been defeated. You are soon hailed by a giant rockman outcast "
"inside the pirate fleet. \"You... you killed him... I can barely belive my "
"eyes! Renegade! I don't know if you realize what you have just done, but by "
"killing Purple Beard, you will now take his place in our legends!\" She then"
" hails all other fleet ships. \"Everyone! Stop attacking the Renegade at "
"once! They are now our leader!\" You are suddunly flooded with hails from "
"every pirate ship in the beacon, all singing songs in your honor. It isn't "
"too long before a small pirate shuttle delivers a box of supplies to you. It"
" seems piracy pays off... sometimes."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:531
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD_WIN_PLAN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue scrapping the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:533
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD_WIN_PLAN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You are almost done scrapping the rest of the ship when you see a sealed "
"room hidden so well you almost missed it. After opening it, you are greated "
"by small hidden clonebay which just finished cloning Purple Beard! After "
"bringing him back to your ship, and letting him heal a bit, he approaches "
"you with a wide grin. \"Renegade! It's... so nice to see you alive and well "
"after our fight...\" He chuckles painfully and taps your shoulder with more "
"strength than you expect from someone his age."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:535
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD_WIN_PLAN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "So was this the plan?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:537
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD_WIN_PLAN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"He nods slowly. \"Now that everyone thinks I kicked the bucket... my legend "
"can finally be put to rest... and... as thanks for giving me a new life... I"
" will help you along your journey... Renegade... or should I say... 'Pirate "
"Legend'...\" He winks and laughs dryly."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:538
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_PURPLE_BEARD_WIN_PLAN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Purple Beard"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:565
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STORE_COALITION\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"As you watch the Coalition vessel break apart, you reflect on what a stupid "
"acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:568
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STORE_COALITION\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:570
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STORE_COALITION\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:573
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STORE_COALITION\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:580
