"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DOGFIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1558
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DOGFIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1565
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DOGFIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"As their last crew falls, you reflect on what a stupid acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" "
"is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1568
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DOGFIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1570
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DOGFIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1573
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DOGFIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1582
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A R.U.E.S. and an MFK Ace ship are in a heated dogfight on this beacon while"
" their respective fleets fight in the background. You could pick a side to "
"fight alongside but that will cause the fleets to also start targeting you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1586
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the R.U.E.S.."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1588
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Coalition ship is caught off guard by your advances. It decides that the"
" rebel ship is a lower threat than you and so turns their weapons towards "
"your ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1591
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1597
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Attack the MFK Ace."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1599
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Rebel manages to disable the coalition's weapons before seeing you "
"aproach. They waste no time before targeting you with their next shot."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1602
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1608
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them and prepare to jump away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1610
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Messing with either side of this conflict is bound to cause issues. It's "
"better to let them destroy each other."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1612
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1616
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1624
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE_COALITION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The R.U.E.S. ship hails you. \"A Federation renegade helping ussss? Now have"
" I sssseen everything! I ssssuppousssse you desssserve a reward.\" The "
"captain chuckles before cutting the feed."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1630
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_COALITION_BATTLE_REBEL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The MFK Ace hails you. \"I can't believe I'm saying this to a Federation "
"dog, but thank you for the help. Those Coalition freaks are a lot tougher "
"than expected. While it pains me to say this, you deserve a reward.\" The "
"captain sighs before cutting the feed."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1641
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PIRATE_ELITE_VS_FEDERATION\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1649
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PIRATE_ELITE_VS_FEDERATION\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1659
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that an elite pirate is in the middle of a dogfight with an elite "
"Federation ship. The pirate is somehow coming out on top while the "
"Federation fleet in the background is struggling to hit them, making the "
"whole situation even more baffling."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1662
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Pirate."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1664
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate captain chuckles as they welcome another challenger with open "
"arms."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1667
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1673
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Don't get involved."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1675
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"That pirate is problably on another level compared to you if it can do loops"
" around an elite federation ship like that. Safer to just ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1677
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1681
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1689
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Federation ship hails you. \"Thank the stars you arrived, Renegade. I "
"have no idea how those pirates were so experienced, fighting them felt like "
"fighting an MFK Ace! We heard reports of other nasty pirates like those "
"around this sector too... Once this is over, I'm going to report the "
"existance of this 'elite pirates' thing to high command, this threat needs "
"to be taken more seriously. Anyways, you deserve a reward for your bravery "
"today, we will also be sure to spread the word of your courage to others.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1694
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_PIRATE_FEDERATION_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1703
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DESTROYER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"As you watch the Coalition vessel break apart, you reflect on what a stupid "
"acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1706
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DESTROYER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1708
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DESTROYER\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1711
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DESTROYER\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1718
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DESTROYER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"As their last crew falls, you reflect on what a stupid acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" "
"is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1721
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DESTROYER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1723
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DESTROYER\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1726
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_DESTROYER\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1736
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you enter this beacon, the ship is flooded with distress calls from the "
"nearby moon. It seems the Coalition fleet here is attacking a mostly "
"defenceless Union research station, with a R.U.E.S. destroyer leading the "
"charge. A few Militia ships are attempting to buy the crew enough time to "
"evacuate, but without help they won't make it."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1740
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the destroyer!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1742
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Coalition ship is caught off guard by the sudden reinforcements. Still "
"they don't miss a beat and turn their weapons towards you. \"A Federation "
"Renegade?! What are you doing here?! You know what, I don't care that "
"command thinks this is a waste of time, I will destroy your ship and then "
"this waste of space in the form of a research station! Then I- I mean *we* "
"will finally have a place to rest after each fight!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1745
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1751
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Don't get involved."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1753
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Attacking the leader of a whole fleet would be a mistake greater than you "
"can afford to do at the moment. Best to just move on and pretend you never "
"saw any of this."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1755
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1759
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1767
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Without the destroyer leading the charge, the rest of the fleet scatters, "
"seemingly under orders to retreat. You are hailed by a Union scientist. "
"\"Thank the heavens you arrived! Our brave security did what they could, but"
" we would have never stood a chance against a whole fleet! Please take this "
"augment; I'm sure it will come in hand in your mission.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1772
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_UNION_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1788
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_DAMAGED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Despite being close enough to be in ASB range from the MFK fleet, this "
"beacon is surprisingly peaceful. The only thing of note is a damaged MFK Ace"
" ship. Though the damage doesn't seem to have been done to any combat-"
"essential areas. They notice you but make no hostile moves."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1792
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_DAMAGED\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the MFK!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1794
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_DAMAGED\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The MFK Ace ship struggles to power itself online for battle, but is quickly"
" able to get its systems online enough to fight you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1797
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_DAMAGED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1803
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_DAMAGED\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1805
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_DAMAGED\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"If they didn't attack you first that means they don't want to fight you. And"
" so, by the same coin, you decide to not fight them either."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1807
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_DAMAGED\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1811
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_DAMAGED\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1820
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ELITE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've defeated the Innovation Auto-ship. The escalation in threat posed by "
"this foe could not be denied, but in the end, it was still nothing more than"
" an infernal machine promptly silenced by your show of force."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1823
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ELITE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1825
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ELITE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the advanced Auto-ship survived the fight. Inside is a"
" functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1828
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ELITE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1837
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"To your surprise you find two auto ships fighting in this rather secluded "
"beacon, a Federation and a Innovation Rebel auto ship. The rebel one, being "
"an elite ship, has the clear upper hand and will certainly destroy the "
"Federation one if not stopped."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1840
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Rebel auto!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1842
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The auto ship swiftly responds to your aggression in kind, aiming their "
"weapons directly at you!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1845
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1851
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1853
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They are just auto ships, one more or one less won't matter in the grand "
"scheme of things."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1855
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1859
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1867
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_AUTO_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Federation auto hails, \"Renegade. Your contributions have been noted "
"and deemed worthy of a: High tier reward.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1880
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_NEUTRAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As the R.U.E.S. fleet looms in the distance, you expect that a fight with a "
"Coalition ship would happen at any moment, yet all that happens is you being"
" hailed by a R.U.E.S. ship. \"Oh for goodnesssss ssssake, *another* "
"Federation sssship?! We jusssst desssstroyed a whole fleet you dumbassssses!"
" You know what? I can't be bothered, you can leave.\" The slug waves you "
"away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1884
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_NEUTRAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "We need to avange the fallen! Attack the Coalition ship!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1886
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_NEUTRAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The slug groans and mumbles some expletives under their breath before "
"powering on their weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1889
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_NEUTRAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1895
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_NEUTRAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1897
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_NEUTRAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"While the death of the Federation crew was a great shame, with the massive "
"fleet in the background it's a terrible idea to attack the smug slug."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1899
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_NEUTRAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1903
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_COALITION_NEUTRAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1913
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ELITE_ESCAPING\"]/gotaway/text"
msgstr ""
"The auto managed to jump away. Like clockwork you can already feel the fleet"
" getting closer to you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1920
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ESCAPING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you jump into this beacon you detect that an FTL drive is "
"starting to charge. When looking around you find an Innovation Rebel auto "
"ship preparing to jump, no doubt heading to warn the rebel fleet if it gets "
"away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1923
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ESCAPING\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "We can't let it escape! Attack them!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1925
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ESCAPING\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The auto ship powers on its weapons but doesn't stop charging its FTL drive."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1928
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ESCAPING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1934
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ESCAPING\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Let it escape."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1936
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_ESCAPING\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Innovation autos are tough nuts to crack; better let it escape than deal "
"with its advanced systems and weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1945
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_ENGINEER_REQUEST\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It's rare to see Technicians outswide their core sectors, but it seems the "
"Rebellion is getting desperate for support if they are willing to call on "
"their help. The Technician ship doesn't attack you though, instead they hail"
" you. \"Renegade, I know this is unorthodox, but we are heavily behind our "
"quotas and we need to raise scrap quickly. We don't have any equipment to "
"sell you but we are willing to let you hire one of our trained personnel.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1948
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_ENGINEER_REQUEST\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Hire their crew."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1950
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_ENGINEER_REQUEST\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Field Technician thanks you and beams abord their crew. They ramble on "
"about the terms of their employment but nothing jumps out to you as "
"predatory so you sign it without much worry."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1958
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_ENGINEER_REQUEST\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Decline their offer."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1960
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_ENGINEER_REQUEST\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Technician seems to start panicking; they weren't expecting you to "
"decline their deal. \"I'm sorry Renegade, but we are too far behind to be "
"able to miss out on a deal like this. Weapons up.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:1963
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_ENGINEER_REQUEST\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

