msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_NEUTRAL_WARZONE_GENERIC_REBEL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find an MFK Ace ship patroling the nearby beacon, though they haven't "
"noticed you yet."

