#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2127
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_UNION\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"As you watch the Coalition vessel break apart, you reflect on what a stupid "
"acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2130
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_UNION\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
