#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2207
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_CRYSTAL_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Crystal ship survived the fight. Inside is a"
" functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2210
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_CRYSTAL_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2217
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_CRYSTAL_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The last of crew of the mighty elite vessel falls to the ground, finally "
"putting an end to this fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2220
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_CRYSTAL_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2222
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_CRYSTAL_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Crystal ship survived the fight. Inside is a"
" functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2225
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_CRYSTAL_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2239
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've managed to take down a Cultivator and their ship, and now the remains"
" are yours to scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2242
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2244
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Vampweed ship survived the fight. Inside is "
"a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2247
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2254
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"You've managed to take down the Cultivator's crew, and now their ship is "
"yours to scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2257
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2259
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Vampweed ship survived the fight. Inside is "
"a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2262
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_ELITE_DISTRESS\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2277
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems this beacon was home of two distinct distress calls, one coming from Sentinel ship and another from a Cultivator. It seems the Federation has requested their aid in retaking the sector, but something must have happened to cause them to turn on each other. They seem to be locked into a deadly duel where the crystal's crew are all almost dead from the boarders while the vampweed ship is threatening to break apart at any moment from all the crystal shots it has taken.\n"
"\n"
"Both ships have seen you already, so refusing to help either would lower your standing with both factions."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2281
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Sentinel."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2283
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Cultivator ship shambles away, attemping to avoid any stray shots, while"
" the Sentinel ship turns its powerful elite weapons against you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2286
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2292
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Cultivator."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2294
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Cultivator quickly beams back their crew, leaving any remaining crystals"
" alive for the time being. Without a second thought they turn their weapons "
"and crew towards you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2297
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2303
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Avoid the dogfight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2305
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"No matter the consequences, it's the far safer bet than fighting either one "
"of those enemies."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2307
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2315
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL_CRYSTAL_WON\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The almost broken Cultivator ship limps back into view after the fight is over, they hail after a short delay. \"Federation renegade, never in a million years would I have thought that we would be actually happy to see one of you lot. We were called here to aid in your war effort, but those damn thick-headed crystals kept wanting to hunt down every god forseken pirate that came across our radar! We wanted them to understand that we were here on a very specific mission but they just wouldn't listen... We tried talking some sense into their thick skulls but... I fear I may have said things I now regret...\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"The Cultivator sighs. \"Well, my ship is almost destroyed and my crew are all gone... Mind if I hitch a ride on your ship for a while? I promise I will let my supperiors know of your deed here today.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2321
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL_CRYSTAL_WON\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2327
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL_VAMPWEED_WON\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The single remaining crew on the Sentinel ship hails you. \"A Federation renegade... I see. I should have expected one of you to be here. This fight... shouldn't have happened. We were supposed to work together, but all those filthy pirates had to do was offer some scrap to those corrupt Vampweeds to look the otherway and get away scot-free every time! We have seen the damage those pirates can do with our own eyes! They single-handedly destroyed an elite Coalition ship in front of us! We have even heard rumors of them having entire fleets at their command now!\"\n"
"\n"
"The crystal sighs. \"I suppose what's done is done... but my crew seem to have given up all their lives to protect me to no avail. My ship is far too damaged to be able to jump again without fear of it cracking at the seams... Would you be willing to let me serve on your ship until I can return to my home sector?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2333
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_VAMPWEED_CRYSTAL_VAMPWEED_WON\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2341
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You quickly find the source of the distress beacon, it seems an Innovation "
"auto ship has been damaged enough to the point where it can't distinguish "
"friend from foe. You could spend some time repairing it but chances are it "
"will attack you if you repair its recognition hardware. Or you could take "
"advantage of its malfunctioning sensors and get it to dispense supplyes to "
"you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2344
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Repair the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2346
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[1]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"The auto ship is repaired successfully without fixing its broken sensors "
"after some time. \"Technician offer. This vessel has been repaired to its "
"full functionalities. Reward is due.\" The auto ship dispenses some supplies"
" before jumping away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2353
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[1]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"After some time you manage to repair the auto ship successfully... maybe too"
" successfully, as now that its sensors are online it quickly points their "
"weapons at you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2357
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[1]/event[2]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2362
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[1]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you attempt to repair the ship, you accidentally must have connected the "
"wrong wires, causing a runaway explosion inside the ship. You are lucky none"
" of your crew were hurt, but it was a close call. Unfortunately not much "
"survived to be scrapped as the explosion almost completely obliterated the "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2369
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Attack the auto!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2371
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Damaged or not, Innovation auto ships are way too dangerous to be left "
"operating, it's safer for everyone if we destroy it before it can harm "
"anyone. The auto ship struggles to power its offensive measures, eventually "
"damaging its own systems in the process. Still, even while damaged, "
"Innovation ships are formidable foes."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2376
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2382
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/text"
msgstr "(Engineer Crew) Repair the auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2384
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Engineer knows exactly what to fix for the ship to give you some "
"tempting supplies before initiating its self destruct protocols, that way it"
" won't be a threat to anyone else."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2391
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/text"
msgstr "(Engi Crew) Repair the auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2393
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Engi isn't used to working with rebel auto ships, and so isn't as "
"efficient at repairing them as Engineers or Technicians, still it manages to"
" repair the ship enough for it to give you some supplies. However midway "
"through the exchange the auto ship detects you as an enemy and powers its "
"offensive weapons to fight you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2397
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2403
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Avoid the auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2405
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The last thing you want to deal with is a malfunctioning auto ship. You keep"
" your distance from it and prepare to jump."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2407
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[5]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2411
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_BROKEN\"]/choice[5]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2420
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_FEDERATION_ELITE_STOLEN\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty Federation ship crumbles to pieces. It's a shame such powerful "
"technology had to be wasted like this..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2422
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_FEDERATION_ELITE_STOLEN\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2424
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_FEDERATION_ELITE_STOLEN\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The shuttle hails you again. \"Thank you, Renegade. I will do my best to "
"explain to my superiors what happened here today. I'm sure they will "
"understand why you destroyed our ship. Feel free to scrap any pieces you "
"might find; you earned it.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2427
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_FEDERATION_ELITE_STOLEN\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2434
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_FEDERATION_ELITE_STOLEN\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"As the last Coalition soldier falls, you can't help but feel a strong sense "
"of justice for avenging all the fallen. Hopefully losing these elite "
"soldiers will slow down the Coalition's plans in this war."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2436
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_FEDERATION_ELITE_STOLEN\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2438
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_FEDERATION_ELITE_STOLEN\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The shuttle hails you again. \"Renegade! You did it! I mean, of course you "
"did, why did I ever doubt you? You not only took out some nasty Coalition "
"soldiers, but you also stopped any plans they would have had with that ship."
" Please, have this weapon and as much scrap as we were carrying!\"."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2442
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_FEDERATION_ELITE_STOLEN\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2458
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PIRATE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find two ships in this beacon, a Unity shuttle and a Unity battleship, "
"with the distress call coming from the shuttle. They hail you. \"Renegade! "
"You gotta help us! A group of Coalition soldiers took over our ship while we"
" were sleeping! If they can infiltrate out ranks then the damage done could "
"be immeasurable! Especially since we were also carrying a large supply of "
"elite spore weapons! If you could keep the ship intact then we would greatly"
" pay you everything we have aboard, but if you have to then we accept the "
"consequences of having our old ship destroyed.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2461
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Battleship!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2463
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"If there's any way you can help the defense of this sector, then that's an "
"opportunity that you have to take. Even if that means fighting against "
"Federation technology."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2466
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PIRATE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2472
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PIRATE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Refuse to help."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2474
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PIRATE\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The shuttle's captain looks devastated. They open their mouth to speak but "
"no words come out. They cut the video feed and you prepare to jump."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2476
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PIRATE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2480
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PIRATE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2489
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The mysterious vessel is destroyed. You scrap its smooth white hull while "
"the rainbow lights continue to flicker in and out of life."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2492
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2497
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The crew of the mysterious vessel is dead. You scrap its smooth white hull "
"while the rainbow lights continue to flicker in and out of life."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2500
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2502
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"To your surprise, you find another person stuffed into the storage of the "
"alien ship. They appear to be under some strange trance that has now begun "
"to slowly wear off. Once they're safe, they agree to join your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2505
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2519
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You jump and find two ships, an EDC ship and a strange white ship with "
"rainbow lights dancing across its hull. The militia ship hails you. "
"\"RENEGADE! PLEASE FOR THE LOVE OF GOD HELP US! THAT SHIP IS ABDUCTING ALL "
"OF OUR CREW! WE TRIED FIGHTING THEM BUT JIM JUST PASSED OUT BEFORE HE COULD "
"EVEN FIRE! I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU DO, JUST KILL IT PLEASE!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2522
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the strange ship!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2524
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You suddenly feel an immense headache coming up as soon as the enemy ship's "
"guns point at you. You have no idea what the hell those things are, but you "
"aren't letting them hurt anyone else!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2527
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2533
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore their request for help."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2535
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The call soon turns silent, only a faint static being heard from the other "
"end. After a few more minutes the strange ship jumps away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2538
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2542
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2550
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN_WON\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The EDC ship hails you. \"Renegade! You actually did it! How the hell did "
"you manage to resist the trance of those weird noodle monsters? I guess that"
" doesn't matter, you are a hero in the EDC's eyes today! Please, take this "
"augment as a token of gratitude, it's something every militia ship is given "
"and greatly help us resist enemy ship suppress fire!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2554
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_SIREN_WON\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2568
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_REBEL\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've destroyed the Rebel Elite's ship: no easy task. It's not enough to "
"impact the fleet though, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2571
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_REBEL\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2573
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_REBEL\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2576
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_REBEL\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2583
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_REBEL\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"You've wiped out the crew of the Rebel Elite: no easy task. It's not enough "
"to impact the fleet though, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2586
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_REBEL\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2588
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_REBEL\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2591
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_REBEL\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2606
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_REBEL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you land, you see a Union ship fleeing from an MFK Ace. The Union"
" ship hails you and begs you to help them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2608
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_REBEL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the MFK Ace!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2610
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_REBEL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you can power your weapons, the MFK Ace manages to land a shot on the"
" Union shuttle right as their shields were down from another volley. You "
"aren't sure if they survived but you can't check right now as the Rebel "
"points their guns at you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2613
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_REBEL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2619
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_REBEL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2621
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_REBEL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It doesn't take long for the shuttle to be destroyed thanks to your "
"inaction. To make things worse, the Rebel now points their weapons at you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2624
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_REBEL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2633
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_COALITION\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"As you watch the Coalition vessel break apart, you reflect on what a stupid "
"acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2636
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_COALITION\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
