"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_COALITION\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2641
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_COALITION\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
