"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_COALITION\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"As their last crew falls, you reflect on what a stupid acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" "
"is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2651
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_DISTRESS_COALITION\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
