"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_COALITION\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you can power your weapons, R.U.E.S. manages to land a shot on the "
"Union shuttle right as their shields were down from another volley. You "
"aren't sure if they survived but you can't check right now as the Coalition "
"ship points its guns at you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2674
