#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2735
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_PIRATE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2745
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_WIN\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the Union crew didn't survive the hit. With a heavy heart you scrap"
" their ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2749
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_WIN\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Union crew is mostly dead, save for a single crew. With their ship "
"unoperable, they ask to join your crew."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2752
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_WIN\"]/event[2]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2757
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_WIN\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Union crew seem to have managed to fix their ship while the fight raged "
"on. It's still quite damaged but it's intact enough to be able to reach the "
"closest outpost. They thank you for your help and give you one of their guns"
" plus some supplies."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2761
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//eventList[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_WARZONE_GENERIC_WIN\"]/event[3]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2792
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_RUES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The R.U.E.S. are only ever seen near either top secret mission or around the"
" Coalition's home base of operations, even seeing one is something not all "
"renegades can say they have done. They are cunning, ruthless and most of "
"all, viscious. Unfortunately one has detected your presence in this beacon "
"and is charging towards you!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2796
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_RUES\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2798
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_RUES\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The R.U.E.S. captain chuckles as they hail you. \"Such a small and pitiful "
"vessel you have. I'm surprised you weren't picked clean by pirates "
"beforehand. Well, let me do what those weakligns couldn't!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2800
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_RUES\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2810
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"No matter how imposing Night's ships are, they lack the discipline and "
"training that other elites tend to get. Still, their dirty tactics clearly "
"failed them today as their ship breaks apart at the seems."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2813
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2815
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Knight ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2821
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Knight crew are extremely resilient and are equipped with the best tech the "
"Kleptocracy has to offer. Still, they die like any others."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2824
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2826
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Knight ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2840
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_KNIGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems Nights must have been taking the Coalition's losses on this sector "
"personally, as he sent a vessel of his personal elite soldiers flanked by a "
"R.U.E.S. fleet! There's no way to avoid this fight either as the Knight is "
"already barreling towards you before you can even react!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2844
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_KNIGHT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2846
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_KNIGHT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Knight chuckles as they hail for just long enough to speak before "
"shutting off the call. \"It sssseemssss you made a... grave misssstake "
"today, renegade.\" You aren't sure if that was a pun or not, but you don't "
"have the time to ponder that as the enemy is already firing in your general "
"direction!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2848
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_KNIGHT\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2858
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"Even the Hive's strongest ships have their limits, and it seems the enemy "
"Bishop has finally reached theirs. With one last crack the ship explodes "
"into pieces."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2861
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2863
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Bishop ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2869
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Mantis Bishops are some of the best warriors the multiverse has to offer, "
"they capture the pwerfect mix of speed and power. No matter how mighty, "
"though, all warriors must fall one day."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2872
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2874
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Bishop ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2888
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_BISHOP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"If there's a battle going on, you can bet your bottom scrap that a Mantis "
"isn't too far behind to join it. Bishops are even more willing and ready to "
"serve their Queen, no matter where and no matter when. Case in point, the "
"Bishop ship charging at you at speeds too high for you to escape easily."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2892
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_BISHOP\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2894
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_BISHOP\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Bishop hails you. \"Renegade! Queen Leikonpliiinakra requested sector "
"captured! Nothing stands in way your majesty's plans! Fight well and best "
"warriors wins!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2896
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_BISHOP\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2906
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_ROCK\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"While Paladin ships might seem indestructable, they can still be cracked "
"open with enough force. There's few people who have managed to destroy a "
"Paladin's hull and lived to tell the tale. Now you are one of them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2909
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_ROCK\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2911
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_ROCK\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Paladin ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2917
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_ROCK\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Just like their ships, Paladins are the toughest and most resistant crew you"
" can ever come across in the multiverse. Some might even think they are "
"immortal given how much punishment they can take without even flinching, and"
" yet here you stand with the enemy ship devoid of life."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2920
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_ROCK\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2922
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_ROCK\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Paladin ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2935
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_PALADIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Theocracy only brings out their Paladin ships when their will needs to "
"be enforced through extreme measures. They crush both the enemy's resistance"
" fighters and their hopes at the same time. They're no slouches in the speed"
" department either, as you can clearly see from the Rock ship barreling "
"towards you at a high enough speed to make any escape impossible."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2939
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_PALADIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2941
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_PALADIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Paladin hails you. \"Bah, just another filty Federation bug that needs "
"squashing. And here I thought we had finally found a worthy challange in "
"this sector of weaklings. You will know the wrath of the Inquisition here "
"today, heretic!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2943
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_PALADIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2953
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_LEECH\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The Amperes are trained explicitly by the Coalition itself, far deadlier "
"than normal Leeches. By destroying this ship, you've probably crippled a "
"good percentage of the Republic's only able soldiers."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2956
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_LEECH\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2958
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_LEECH\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Leech ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2964
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_LEECH\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The Amperes are trained explicitly by the Coalition itself, and are far "
"deadlier than normal Leeches. By killing all their crew, you've probably "
"crippled a good percentage of the Republic's only able soldiers."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2967
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_LEECH\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2969
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_LEECH\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Leech ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2982
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_AMPERE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Coalition must be getting desperate if they are bringing their Amperes "
"to the fight. While their ships are quite formidable, their crew aren't "
"anywhere near experienced enough to handle the same heat as other elites of "
"the faction. Still, that doesn't mean they don't occasionally do something "
"right, like catching you off guard right now and forcing a fight."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2986
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_AMPERE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2988
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_AMPERE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Ampere hails you. \"I'm tired of having to avoid you Renegades everytime"
" we need to scout a beacon! Time for you to finally fear our alliance!\" The"
" ship's weapons power up to engage you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:2990
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_COALITION_AMPERE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3006
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've destroyed the Rebel Elite's ship: no easy task. It's not enough to "
"impact the fleet though, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3009
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3011
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3017
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"You've wiped out the crew of the Rebel Elite: no easy task. It's not enough "
"to impact the fleet though, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3020
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3022
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3035
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_MFK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Rebellion's assault on this sector is still at full force, even if they "
"also need to defend it from the Coalition. No expense is spared on making "
"absolutely sure the sector is theirs. This seems to be mainly in the form of"
" flooding the sector with MFK Aces. Speaking of which, one seems to have "
"already found you. You're cornered you before you can even charge your jump."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3039
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_MFK\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3041
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_MFK\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The MFK Ace hails you. \"Federation scum! This sector is ours now and "
"there's nothing you or those filthy aliens can do to stop our plans! For the"
" Rebellion!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3043
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_MFK\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3053
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've defeated a technician vessel, impressively. Though they may simply be"
" menial workers in the eyes of Wentworth Innovations, their ships are "
"considerably well-armed, and successfully defeating one in combat is no "
"small feat."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3056
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3058
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Technician ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3064
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"You've killed all of the technician vessel's crew, impressively. Though they"
" may simply be menial workers in the eyes of Wentworth Innovations, their "
"crew's drones are surprisingly competetent in combat, and successfully "
"defeating one is no small feat."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3067
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3069
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Technician ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3078
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Rebellion rarely sends their Field Technicians into combat, especially "
"in disputed sectors. Their combat abilities are simply not on par with their"
" MFK Aces or even elite Rebels. However, it seems the Rebellion is desperate"
" enough for control of this sector to send a Technician ship to take you "
"out."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3082
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3084
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Field Technician hails you. \"I apologise for what we need to do, but "
"unfortunately we have been given very firm instructions to make sure you "
"won't stop any plans our bosses have. Wentowrth Innovations would appreciate"
" your cooperation if you just depowered your systems and made our life "
"easier.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3086
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3099
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_AUTO\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3101
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_AUTO\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Innovation Auto ship survived the fight. Inside is"
" a functional sentry weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3110
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_ESTATE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Innovation auto ships are some of the finest auto ships that the Rebellion "
"has to offer, with the only possible exception being a super secret auto "
"class that no one has ever seen firsthand and is only vaguely alluded to in "
"some confidential Rebel papers. Built by the most skilled Wentworth Field "
"Technicians, these elite ships can hold their own even against powerful "
"battleships. Hopefully you are prepared to fight them since one is charging "
"straight at you!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3114
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_ESTATE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3116
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_ESTATE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Innovation Auto hails you. \"Federation ship. You have been scanned and "
"deemed a threat to our future operations. There will be no mercy. Death to "
"the Federation! For the Rebellion!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3118
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_REBEL_ESTATE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3136
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_UNITY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Federation has been on their back foot ever since the Rebels first "
"invaded the sector. The subsequent invasion of the Coalition only stoked the"
" flames of chaos in their already disorganised defences. It seems that the "
"stress of the whole situation is finally getting to some of the soldiers, as"
" a Unity vessel just mistook you for a hired Rebel mercenary."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3140
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_UNITY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3142
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_UNITY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Human soldier in charge of the ship hails you. \"The Rebels are hiring "
"Renegades now?! Great, that's just freaking great! Hear me, mercenary scum, "
"we will not kowtow to neither the Rebels, nor the Coalition, nor whatever "
"other faction tries to break us! Our unity won't be so easily broken!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3144
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_UNITY\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3155
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STEALTH\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The Federation has precious few stealth ships in service, and eliminating "
"one is a major blow to their special operations. But your mission is more "
"important, and you waste little time in salvaging the remains."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3158
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STEALTH\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3160
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STEALTH\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the stealth ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3166
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STEALTH\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Federation stealth ships have some of the best soldiers the Federation has "
"to offer, and so what you have done here today will unfortunately cause "
"severe repercussions for future plans of the Federation."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3169
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STEALTH\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3171
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STEALTH\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the stealth ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3180
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_STEALTH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are surprised to see a Federation stealth ship out in the open like "
"this. It seems your arrival in this beacon has disrupted whatever the "
"captain of the ship was planning, because they are now heading towards you "
"with their weapons online and cloaking system charged!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3184
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_STEALTH\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3186
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_STEALTH\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The captain of the stealth ship hails you. \"You! Of course command would "
"send some of you renegade Morons to 'assist' with retaking this sector! We "
"told them over and over that we didn't need any help whatsoever! If "
"anything, you are an active liability! So screw it! If command won't listen "
"to reason, then I will make sure you won't set us back any more than your "
"presence already has!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3188
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_STEALTH\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3198
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_MILITIA\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The EDC is one of the few forces capable of defending civilian sectors, and "
"they aren't exactly common. The loss of this ship will certainly have "
"negative effects on the Militia."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3201
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_MILITIA\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3203
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_MILITIA\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Militia ship survived the fight. Inside is a"
" functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3209
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_MILITIA\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The EDC soldiers might not have the most high-grade training when compared "
"to elite Federation personnel, but they can still put up one hell of a fight"
" when push comes to shove."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3212
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_MILITIA\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3214
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_MILITIA\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Militia ship survived the fight. Inside is a"
" functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3223
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_EDC\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The EDC or 'Elite Defence Cadre' is the best of the best that the militia "
"has to offer. Under the command of Senator Wright, the EDC might be "
"underequipped when compared to the Federation's Unity ships, but that "
"doesn't mean they should be understimated. You attempt to hail the nearby "
"EDC ship but all you get is a warning shot in your general direction."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3227
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_EDC\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3229
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_EDC\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The captain of the EDC ship hails you. \"Bah! More reckless Renegades "
"putting their noses where they don't belong! Do you think we will ever "
"forgive your type after the Rusting Hulks incident? Not a chance! Weapons "
"up, criminal!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3231
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_EDC\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3241
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGI\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"Harmony ships are the Harmony's main line of defense against outside "
"threats. The destruction of this ship today will surely leave them open to "
"harsher attacks."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3244
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGI\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3246
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGI\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Engi ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional drone, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3252
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGI\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"With the death of the Engi Defenders there are now fewer ships to protect "
"the Harmony from true threats, but you can't run away from every fight. You "
"salvage the remains of the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3255
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGI\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3257
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGI\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Engi ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional drone, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3270
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HARMONY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Federation is clearly not going down quietly in this sector, and to "
"prove it they've even received the support of Harmony elite ships. It's "
"strange to see these ships out here, given the fact that Engi that stray too"
" far from their links tend to end up needing to be recycled. Maybe that has "
"something to do with this specific Harmony ship deeming you a threat as it "
"advances towards you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3274
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HARMONY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3276
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HARMONY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Defender hails you. \"Ship scanned. Deemed to be a: Renegade. Risk for "
"harmful unplanned actions = 98%. Risk exceeds acceptable parameters. "
"Solution: Eliminate threat.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3278
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_HARMONY\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3288
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ZOLTAN\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"So much for peacekeeping. The Ministry struggles to keep its Peacekeeper "
"task force up to par with the chaotic threats in the Multiverse, and you "
"destroying their ships certainly won't help that."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3291
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ZOLTAN\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3293
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ZOLTAN\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Zoltan ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3299
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ZOLTAN\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Peacekeepers are the most strict and disciplined soldiers in the whole "
"Federation. They might not be the most durable or the most powerful, but "
"what they lack in specialization they more than make up for in versitility."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3302
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ZOLTAN\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3304
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ZOLTAN\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Zoltan ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3317
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PEACE_KEEPER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Ministry didn't waste any time in helping the Federation retake this "
"sector, sending out waves upon waves of their best soldiers for the war "
"effort, although it's clear their intentions are far from autruistic. If "
"they help the Federation retake the sector, the Ministry will be able to "
"claim jurisdiction and control over it, since their presence in the sector "
"is the heaviest out of all Federation allies. It seems like the Ministry "
"isn't going to wait around for the war to be finished before securing the "
"sector, as one of their Peacekeeper ships has cornered you and is powering "
"on their weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3321
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PEACE_KEEPER\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3323
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PEACE_KEEPER\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Peacekeeper hails you. \"Renegade, you are under arrest for trespassing "
"into a sector labled as an 'Active Warzone' by the Ministry, as described "
"under the Military Cooperation Act 66-T, Section 11-A. Do not resist or risk"
" immediate execution.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3325
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PEACE_KEEPER\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3335
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ORCHID\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've managed to take down a Praetor and their ship, and now the remains "
"are yours to scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3338
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ORCHID\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3340
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ORCHID\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Orchid ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3346
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ORCHID\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Praetors aren't easily replaceble, and the Gathering have enough enemies as "
"is. Hopefully the loss of these highly-trained soldiers won't spell doom for"
" the Gathering in the long run."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3349
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ORCHID\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3351
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ORCHID\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Orchid ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3364
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PRAETOR\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"While generally a peaceful race, the Floral Orchids are no strangers to war."
" Their elite ships have powerful kernel weapons that can easily swing the "
"tide of battle by themselves. Unfortunately, either by a miscommunication or"
" enemy deception, this Praetor has deemed you the threat they were assigned "
"to take out!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3368
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PRAETOR\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3370
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PRAETOR\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Praetor hails you. \"Renegade, I hope you don't take this personally, "
"but high command has ordered you to be removed from the frontlines by force."
" We'd rather not escalate this situation but if you resist we will be forced"
" to neutralize you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3372
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_PRAETOR\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3380
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The war for this sector has truly unearthed the true threat that the "
"unaffiliated  pirates can pose. Their use of highly illigal and dangerous "
"weapons combined with their truly reckless abandon when it comes to picking "
"their targets makes them a threat that should be taken as seriously as the "
"MFK Aces or R.U.E.S.. It seems you are now one of their targets, as an elite"
" pirate has caught you off guard!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3384
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weapons up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3386
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate hails you \"My my, what a fancy ship you got there. I'm sure it "
"would fetch a ton of scrap in the right hands. And then, with that kinda "
"money, I could finally earn Purple Beard's admiration! Time to die, "
"Renegade!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3388
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_ELITE_WARZONE_PIRATE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3413
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you arrive you notice a huge crowd of Federation ships stationed around a Unity station. As you cycle through the Federation Military bands, you find the one that all the ships seem to be using to communicate.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"There seems to be a meeting going on between a human soldier, a Defender Engi, a Peace-keeper Zoltan and what seems to be a high-ranking Federation official. The soldier is the first to speak. \"You must be MAD, Lieutenant Kely! We don't have the equipment to fight off their elites! We would all be obliterated in seconds! Even if Luminus was able to gather a few of his Ministry friends to help us, a single MFK Ace would blast us back to the Stone Ages!\"\n"
"\n"
"The Lieutenant sighs, her short faded green-dyed hair almost fully obscured by her helmet. \"I understand your concerns, Officer Jan, but we are running out of options fast. This package is *essential*. We can't allow either the Rebels or the Coalition to get their hands on the full machine, no matter the cost.\" Her voice is tired but she maintains her resolve.\n"
"\n"
"The Defender engi speaks, their voice changing pitch every other sentence. \"Affirmative. However, risk of failure exceeds safe parameters. Probability of total failure = almost guaranteed.\" The Peacekeeper groans. \"Look, can we speed this up? If we are about to die anyways then we might as well just get it over with.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3422
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Offer to help."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3424
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Kely looks at you, clearly startled by your interjection. \"Ah, you must be the Renegade we hired for this reality. I suppose you are better-equipped than any of us at the moment. Very well, I will send you the coordinates to the first piece. There are two in total; once you have both of them, you will need to deliver them to my superiors. Don't worry about the specifics; once you get the first piece, you will be directed to the other one.\"\n"
"\n"
"The peace-keeper stares at you for a moment. \"If you want to go on this mission then the least we can do is offer you something to help you fight off whatever foes you come across. We can't afford to give you everything but feel free to pick any of our offers.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3428
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "We need crew."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3430
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Lieutenant sighs. \"I'm sorry, but we don't have anyone that we can "
"spare. Is there anything else you need?\" However, before you can answer, "
"Officer Jan gets up from his chair. \"Bullshit, I'm still here and I'll be "
"damned if I just stand around waiting for you to be destroyed by a roaming "
"pirate!\" Jan beams himself aboard your ship, much to the annoyance of Kely,"
" who sighs exasperatedly. \"Very well then... Let me give you the "
"coordinates.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3431
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Jan"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3436
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We need a weapon."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3438
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Lieutenant nods \"We received a shipment of beam weapons recently. We "
"have too many of them for the few Unity ships that can properly use them.\" "
"She beams the beam weapon into your ship and then hands you the coordinated."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3444
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "We need a drone."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3446
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Engi perks up. \"This unit's vessel has been outfitted with an excessive"
" amount of combat drones. Surplus equipment raises chances for pirate "
"attacks by: 50%.\" The Engi beams a combat drone aboard your ship while Kely"
" gives you the coordinates."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3452
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "We need a combat augment."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3454
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan smiles. \"I see you are a person of good taste, Renegade. The art"
" of combat augments is one that has been lost recently. I make and sell "
"augments as a hobby, but I can spare one for you as thanks for getting us "
"out of this pickle.\" The Zoltan transfers the augment to you while Kely "
"sends over the coordinates."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3462
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore the conversation and move on."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3464
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As dire as things are, your mission is as important as theirs. You charge "
"your FTL and prepare to jump."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3466
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3470
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3480
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_CRUISER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The massive MFK Ace ship cracks apart as its artillery attempts to shoot one"
" last volley, only for its missiles to jam, causing a huge explosion in the "
"remaining front of the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3483
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_CRUISER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3488
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_CRUISER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The MFK Aces do their best to hold on to their powerful vessel but at some "
"point it becomes clear which side will be winning. To your surprise, all the"
" remaining MFK Aces get into escape pods and flee, leaving the remaining "
"soldiers alone to deal with your angry crew. It isn't long before they "
"either surrender or die protecting the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3491
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_CRUISER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3500
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "Location of the first part of the machine."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3501
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Nothing left of interest."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3511
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You reach the coordinates for the first half of whatever machine Lieutenant Kely was so worried about securing. To your surprise you not only find an MFK Ace ship here, but a rebel cruiser painted in MFK Ace colors! It seems this cruiser destroyed a Unity ship before you arrived and was about to collect a strangely reinforced metal crate. That must be the package you are after!\n"
"\t\t\n"
"They hail you. \"Hah! I was told some Federation clown would come and try stop us or save that poor sap that we just destroyed. Frankly, I thought they would have at least sent a fleet against us. What is this pathetic excuse for a ship?\" The Rebel laughs before her tone gets more serious. \"Alright, Feddy boy, let me be crystal clear here. You either walk away and pretend you never saw us, or we will blast your ship to atoms, got it?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3517
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "We won't back down! We need that package!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3519
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You power on your weapons while the enemy ship does the same. This won't be "
"pretty, but you can't risk losing that package!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3522
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3528
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Vance Prime) \"Halt, soldier! I order you back away from the wreck and "
"allow us to operate in peace!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3530
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The captain blinks, their eyes almost bulging out of their socket. \"V-Vance"
" Prime?! I-I'm so sorry sir! W-We will leave you be at once!\" The Rebel "
"stutters before jumping away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3533
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3539
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Do as they say and back away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3541
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Rebel captain laughs before taking the metal box and jumping away. You "
"pray whatever was inside of it doesn't end up spelling the doom of the "
"Federation..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3544
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3548
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3556
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_1_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"With the Rebel ship dealt with, you are free to secure the crate. As you "
"bring it aboard your ship, you notice a place for you to insert your "
"Federation ID into. After doing so, the crate verifies you as a member of "
"the Federation and uploads the next set of coordinates into your ship's map "
"system. You decide to open the crate, only to find what seems to be parts of"
" a gun, one that seems to have a shallow resemblence to the Vulcan, just "
"much bigger. It's currently unusable though, since the other half is "
"necessary for the gun to actually fire."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3566
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_CRUISER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The mighty R.U.E.S. cruiser splits in half. Pheromones leak uncontrolably "
"even as the slug gel tries to keep most of the ship together. Eventually, "
"even the gel isn't enough to keep the ship together and it collapses."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3569
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_CRUISER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3574
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_CRUISER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The last to fall is unsurprisingly the Paladin, their extremely durable body"
" making them seem invincible... almost. There's no escape attempt this time;"
" the crew goes down with the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3577
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_CRUISER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3586
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "Location of the second part of the machine."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3587
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Nothing left of interest."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3597
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You reach the coordinates for the second half of this strange weapon only to find another Unity ship, this time a battleship, intact but completely inert. You also see a massive R.U.E.S. cruiser, armed and ready to engage with you. However, instead of attacking right away, they hail you.\n"
"\n"
"\"Oh my goodnesssss! Issss that a little Federation sssship wanting to 'avenge' their dead friendssss?!\" The Knight captain burst out laughing. \"That'ssss the cutesssst thing I have sssseen all day! You are a funny persssson, Federation renegade. I like funny people. You can leave now, unlesssss you want to end up like your friendssss over there.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3603
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_1\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "We will make you pay for what you did!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3605
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_1\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The slug chuckles before their expression hardens. \"Fine, your funeral.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3608
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_1\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3614
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_1\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"We don't have the first half of the gun. Getting the second half would be "
"pointless without it."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3618
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_LEIKONPLIIINAKRA_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Leikonpliiinakra) Leikonpliiinakra demands to speak!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3620
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_LEIKONPLIIINAKRA_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Noble warriors! This is your Queen speaking! I demand you vacate this beacon immediately!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"The Knight captain freezes. This is the first time you have ever seen a Knight completely out of their element. \"O-Of coursssse, Your Highnesssss! We will leave right away!\" The captain does as ordered and jumps away, giving you free acess to the wreck."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3625
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_LEIKONPLIIINAKRA_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3631
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_NIGHTS_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Nights) Nights demands to speak!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3633
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_NIGHTS_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Hey! SSSSoldier! Take your fancy sssship and get the hell out of here!\"\n"
"\n"
"The Knight captain freezes before nodding violently. \"O-Of coursssse, Your Highnesssss! We will leave right away!\" The captain does as ordered and jumps away, giving you free acess to the wreck."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3638
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_NIGHTS_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3644
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_TYRDEO_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/text"
msgstr "(Tyrdeo) Ask to speak."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3646
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_TYRDEO_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Excuse me, but I'm Tyrdeo, the President of the Republic. I'm sure you are aware that the Coalition soldiers cannot threaten their leaders without severe consequences. If you were to leave, I would be willing to 'forget' this little event.\"\n"
"\n"
"The Knight captain freezes before gulping and nodding slowly. \"O-Of coursssse, Your Excellency. We will leave right away.\" The captain does as ordered and jumps away, giving you free acess to the wreck."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3651
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_HAS_TYRDEO_AND_GATLING_ONE\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3657
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Do as they say and back away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3659
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The captain grins 'ear' to 'ear' before their crew takes a metal crate from "
"inside the empty Federation battleship and jumps away without another word."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3662
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3666
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3674
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_2_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"With the R.U.E.S. Cruiser out of your way, you are free to investigate the "
"Federation battleship and recover the other half of the strange weapon. You "
"find a metal box almost identical to the first one. You bring it aboard and "
"unlock it the same way you did with the other half. The verification process"
" is slow but it eventually unlocks and gives you the final coordinates, "
"pointing to a nearby Federation outpost. Whoever is in there will be able to"
" re-assemble whatever super weapon this thing is."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3684
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PIRATE_ELITE_KESTREL_CRUISER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"It's a shame to have to destroy a cruiser that certainly must have had quite"
" the story, but in life-or-death scenarios, history doesn't matter as much "
"as you staying alive."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3687
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PIRATE_ELITE_KESTREL_CRUISER\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3692
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PIRATE_ELITE_KESTREL_CRUISER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The trail of misery these pirates must have left in their wake is "
"uncountable. How many hundreds of ships did they rob, de-crew, or destroy "
"before they met their ends at your hands? You have no idea, but at least "
"they can't hurt anyone else anymore."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3695
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_PIRATE_ELITE_KESTREL_CRUISER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3704
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "Location of the Federation outpost needed to fix the gun."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3705
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "Explored location. Nothing left of interest."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3715
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you reach the Federation outpost given by the coordinates, you are shocked by what you see: a Unity Kestrel that has been somehow commandeered by pirates! Unity Kestrels are rare enough to see outside of Universe 0's mega shipyards, but to see one fall prey to unaffiliated  pirates is a once-in-a-lifetime event.\n"
"\n"
"Unfortunately, it doesn't seem like the Kestrel is alone, as you can see a few pirate fleets attacking the few remaining Unity fleet ships. If you were to guess, another faction must have attacked this outpost before the pirates because there's no way unaffiliated pirates could overpower a well-defended Unity outpost.\n"
"\n"
"You are hailed by the outpost's captain. \"A Renegade? What are you doing here?\" You explain to the captain of the outpost about your mission to deliver the weapon parts. She seems relieved once she finally realizes what you are talking about. \"Oh thank the stars the gun didn't fall prey to the Rebels or the Coalition! Look, we will gladly let you keep the gun once it's repaired, but please help us first! We think the leader of this attack is in the Kestrel, since it's where most of the radio waves are coming from. Please take them out by whatever means necessary!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3724
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the Kestrel!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3726
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You are suddenly hailed by the Kestrel as you aproach it. On screen is a man who is likely the captain of the ship. \"Ohohoho! Another challanger joins the ring, eh? Well if today isn't my lucky day! I always wanted to fight a Renagade! Now come! Let's battle this out, cruiser on cruiser!\" \n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"Before the battle can start, however, you see a Unity ship, a Peace-Keeping ship, a Federation ship, and a Harmony ship all arrive together. You are hailed by the Unity ship and on screen is Kely! \"Renegade! Thank goodness you are OK! Our station was unfortunately destroyed by a fleet of MFK Aces, but we all managed to escape. We heard of a pirate attack and came here to try and help them but it seems our paths crossed once more. We will help defend the outpost; focus on fighting off the Kestrel!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3731
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3737
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/text"
msgstr "(Purple Beard) Purple Beard wants to hail the pirates."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3739
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Hear me!... If you value... your lives... I suggest... you stand down... and leave this place! All of you!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"There's silence on your comms for several seconds before the captain of the Kestrel replies, their voice shakey and unsure. \"Oh... shit... Fellas! Everyone scram!\" The comm systems erupt with the sounds of people panicking, and just like that every pirate has left the area without saying another word. You look at Purple Beard, who seems proud of what he has just done, for once."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3744
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3750
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "This gun is too important to back off now."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3756
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL_WIN_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It doesn't take long for the last few remaining pirates to leave the scene. The few that stay to fight are quickly captured or eliminated.\n"
"\n"
"You are hailed by the outpost. \"Renegade! I-I can't believe my eyes! They all scattered! I thought most of them would have stayed and fought; they clearly had the numbers advantage! But I guess this shows that you can never fully predict what a pirate will do. We normally don't give this much away for good deeds, but I think you earned some extra special compensation today!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3762
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL_WIN_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_2\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "We were glad to help, but what about the gun?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3764
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL_WIN_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_2\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"O-Oh! Right right right! Sorry, I almost forgot! Please, come inside our outpost! We will fix up that gun and, as a gesture of good will, you can keep it and use it as you see fit!\" You dock your ship on the outpost alongside Kely and her friends. You two meet in the outpost and talk while your gun is assembled. Once it's finished, Kely herself offers to install the gun on your ship; apparently, she used to be a engineer before the war.\n"
"\n"
"Once everything is setup, you bid farewell to the outpost and return to your ship. You have a feeling the word of your deeds here will spread far and wide."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3773
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL_WIN_PURPLE_BEARD\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_2\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "We were glad to help!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3779
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as the Kestrel falls, all the pirate ships suddenly stop for a few seconds. For a moment you worry that they will try to avenge their leader, but thankfully instead they all scatter, problably seeing the way the fight is going to end.\n"
"\n"
"You are hailed by the outpost. \"Renegade! I-I can't believe my eyes! They all scattered! I mean, I thought they would be easier to defeat without their leader but I wouldn't have ever guessed that they would disband on the spot! Shows you that you can never trust a pirate to have your back. We normally don't give this much away for good deeds, but I think you earned some extra special compensation today!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3786
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_2\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "We were glad to help, what about the gun though?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3788
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_2\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"O-Oh! Right right right! Sorry, I almost forgot! Please, come inside our outpost! We will fix up that gun and, as a gesture of good will, you can keep it and use it as you see fit!\" You dock your ship on the outpost alongside Kely and her friends. You two meet in the outpost and talk while your gun is assembled. Once it's finished, Kely herself offers to install the gun on your ship; apparently, she used to be a engineer before the war.\n"
"\n"
"Once everything is setup, you bid farewell to the outpost and return to your ship. You have a feeling the word of your deeds here will spread far and wide."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3797
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_FEDERATION_GATLING_PART_FINAL_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_UNITY_GATLING_PARTS_2\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "We were glad to help!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3804
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've destroyed the Rebel Elite's ship: no easy task. It's not enough to "
"impact the fleet though, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3807
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3809
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3815
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"You've wiped out the crew of the Rebel Elite: no easy task. It's not enough "
"to impact the fleet though, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3818
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3820
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3833
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems you aren't alone on this beacon, as an MFK Ace ship is parked close by. Strangely, their weapons remain offline though they seem to spot you. Instead of a fight, they hail you. \"Renegade! I'm so glad you were the one that found me and not some Coalition dog or strict Federation soldier. Look, let's not waste your time here and get straight to the point. I do not want to be here and fight this endless war for someone I've never met nor care about. I want O U T, do you get me? We saw a few MFK Ace pirates when fighting around in this sector, and we believe that a pirate's life might be just what we need.\"\n"
"\n"
"The rebel clears their throat before speaking again. \"This ship and crew... well, they became my new home after we left Universe 1, and I can't bear to leave them behind. So I've been scouting ahead, asking the right people the right questions, and I found a particular beacon that doesn't have any Rebel presence on it. If you could bring us there undetected then we can find a way to exit this sector without command even realizing we were gone. We won't need all the guns we got from the ships we destroyed here once we are free, so we plan to compensate you really well once this is over. So... what do you say, renegade?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3838
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Offer to help them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3840
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The MFK grins and nods. \"Good choice, Renegade. We will follow you but we "
"will be about a jump behind so no one sees us working together. It wouldn't "
"look good on your resume if your 'friends' saw you working with the 'enemy'."
" Good luck, Renegade. See you at the beacon... hopefully.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3845
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We aren't helping any Rebels!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3847
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The MFK Ace growls and shuts down the call before their weapons finally come"
" to life."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3850
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3859
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_FEDERATION_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"Unity ships aren't easy to replace, and with the Federation already on the "
"back foot of the war, this loss will end up having much worse consequences "
"than expected."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3862
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_FEDERATION_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3864
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_FEDERATION_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Federation ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3867
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_FEDERATION_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3874
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_FEDERATION_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Eliminating allied Federation personnel, especially Elite ones, is highly "
"contrary to your mission, but that doesn't mean you're beyond salvaging the "
"remains."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3877
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_FEDERATION_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3879
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_FEDERATION_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Elite Federation ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3882
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_FEDERATION_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3893
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've destroyed the Rebel Elite's ship: no easy task. It's not enough to "
"impact the fleet, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3896
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3898
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3901
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3908
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"You've wiped out the crew of the Rebel Elite: no easy task. It's not enough "
"to impact the fleet, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3911
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3913
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3916
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3931
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"The MFK Ace wants help leaving the sector. They promised a big reward if you"
" can help them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3940
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You reach the beacon the Rebel pointed to only to find it being host to a "
"huge skirmish between the Federation and MFK Aces. You attempt to hail the "
"ship you were leading but it seems you were too late as they jump right "
"after you land. At first you hope no one else noticed you or the Rebel but a"
" Unity ship quickly notices you two. \"Rebel! This is the end of the line "
"for you! Come on Renegade, let's kill this fascist!\" The Unity ship moves "
"to attack the Rebel, leaving you with only two choices... It seems the only "
"ship that noticed you two was the Unity ship, meaning you can either betray "
"the rebels or destroy the Federation ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3944
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tully\"]/text"
msgstr "(Tully) Pretend the MFK Ace is a spy."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3946
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tully\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Brave Federation soldier! This Rebel ship is one of our best spies! Power down your weapons and allow them to leave the area!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"The Unity captain is a bit confused at first but quickly grins and nods. \"Ooooh I see what you mean! Great plan, Admiral! We will go back to kicking some Rebel ass. You do whatever you feel like you have to, we won't get on your way!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3950
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tully\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3952
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tully\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"With the Unity ship out of your hide, the way is clear for the Rebel to "
"escape. They hail you. \"Renegade! You didn't tell us that you had Admiral "
"Freaking Tully aboard your ship! How the hell did you manage that?! Anyways,"
" I belive it's time that we part ways. Here's the weapon as promised. Also, "
"while we were following you, one of my best soldiers asked if they could "
"join your crew. It seems piracy isn't the life they want, and I would rest "
"easier knowing they can be happy in the Federation. Have a good life "
"Renegade, and thank you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3960
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Hold your end of the bargain and defend the MFK Ace by attacking the "
"Federation ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3962
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You use the Unity ship's distraction to your advantage and manage to hit "
"their communication systems before they could react. Hopefully this will "
"prevent them from calling backup. The MFK Ace ship stays away from the "
"fight, hoping to blend in with the wrecked ships."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3965
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3971
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Betray the Rebel and attack them alongside the Unity ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3973
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The MFK Ace is visibly betrayed, their shock quickly turning to anger as "
"they turn on their weapons at max power. The Unity ship prepares to send a "
"backup signal to the nearby fleet, but the MFK decides to do the same."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3976
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3984
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT_FEDERATION_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"With the Unity ship down, the way is clear for the Rebel to escape. They "
"hail you. \"Renegade! You are alive! I mean- Of course you are! Your type "
"doesn't go down easy huh? Anyways, I belive it's time that we part ways. "
"Here's the weapon as promised. Also, while we were following you, one of my "
"best soldiers asked if they could join your crew. It seems piracy isn't the "
"life they want, and I would rest easier knowing they can be happy in the "
"Federation. Have a good life Renegade, and thank you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3990
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_REBEL_ESCAPE_EXIT_REBEL_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It pains you to have to dispose to someone you promised to protect, but you "
"couldn't risk becoming an enemy of the Federation, not in this hell hole. "
"The Unity ship hails you. \"Good fighting, renegade! Command will be proud "
"of what we acomplished here today! Here, we had quite the surplus of weapons"
" from all the ships we scrapped; I'm sure you can find a good use for "
"this.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:3998
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/gotaway/text"
msgstr ""
"Whatever secrets that ship had will remain a mystery. All you hope is that "
"this loss won't spell the end to the Federation's efforts on this sector..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4001
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The strange ship's hull cracks and splinters open, leaking copious amounts "
"of nebula gas as it collapses. It seems they were the reason for this out-"
"of-place nebula cloud in the sector. You manage to find a weapon that "
"survived the ship's destruction but whatever information it had is gone for "
"good."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4006
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"The enemy crew seemed weirdly on edge as they fought you; even the slug "
"didn't seem keen on quips or insults. Whatever mission they were on must "
"have been quite important."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4009
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4017
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You wonder why there's a singular beacon in the whole sector that's inside an out-of-place nebula. According to your database, this sector wasn't meant to even have any nebula-covered beacons. You start exploring this strange place when you see an even stranger R.U.E.S. ship in the distance. The nebula is too thick to make out any details but the silhouette isn't one from a ship you recognise.\n"
"\n"
"You approach the ship to get a better look at it, but before you can hail it, the ship seems to notice you and starts backing away. It isn't long before its FTL drive starts charging."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4023
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack them!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4025
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"While the ship might act evasive, that doesn't mean it's invulnerable. When "
"their crew realizes they won't be able to escape so easily, the ship's "
"weapons power on, though their FTL drive doesn't stop charging. If you want "
"whatever secrets it has you need to dispose of their crew before they run "
"away!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4028
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4034
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_mantis_queen\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Leikonpliiinakra) Leikonpliiinakra stays silent and refuses to appear on "
"the feed."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4038
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/text"
msgstr "(Nights) You tried to ask Nights but he's nowhere to be found."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4042
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tyrdeo\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Tyrdeo) Tyrdeo runs away from the room the moment the strange ship appears "
"in your radar and hides in his cabin, refusing to get out until you leave "
"the beacon."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4046
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Let them escape."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4048
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Whatever that ship is, it doesn't want any trouble with you, so you don't "
"want any trouble with it either."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4051
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[5]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4055
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER\"]/choice[5]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4063
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As the ship goes empty, you take the opportunity to give the strange vessel "
"a thorough search. After a while you find the captain's quarters and inside "
"are the coordinates to a hidden beacon in the sector, one that isn't in any "
"maps you know about. You punch the coordinates into your ship's navigation "
"systems and prepare to leave."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4070
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ANCIENT_AUTO_RUINS\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've destroyed the odd auto ship. Its powerful weapons felt like something"
" out of this world, but it seems nothing can stop you now."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4073
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ANCIENT_AUTO_RUINS\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4075
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ANCIENT_AUTO_RUINS\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the strange auto ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a highly advanced weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4078
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ANCIENT_AUTO_RUINS\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4089
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "The location of the coordinates from the strange ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4098
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you reach the strange unmarked beacon, you see a whole fleet of destroyed"
" ships streching as far as your eyes can see. They all look completely "
"foreign to anything you've come across before, with their strange "
"construction style and odd dark materials. Soon, however, you realize you "
"aren't the only thing active in this graveyard of ships, as a strange white "
"and pink auto ship emerges from inside one of the fleet ships. It doesn't "
"attack you yet, but it doesn't hail you either."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4102
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Attack ther ship! Whatever's inside those broken ships must be worth "
"protecting!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4104
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship's lights shine brightly, almost blinding you, before it powers an "
"array of highly futuristic-looking equipment. Whatever this ship is, it "
"isn't messing around!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4107
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4113
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Avoid the strange ship and hope it doesn't attack you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4115
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You slowly back away from the auto ship, and after a tense few minutes, the "
"other ship backs away too and flies back inside the fleet."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4117
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4121
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4129
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"With the auto ship disposed of, you are free to explore this strange place "
"for as much time as you have before the fleet closes in. You spend a few "
"hours exploring all acessible fleet ships, and in the end you find a single "
"ship with an untouched cargo bay."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4131
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4133
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Inside the cargo bay you find 3 pedestals, one with a powerful looking gun, one with a extremely advanced looking drone, and another with some kind of augment installer that looks advanced beyond anything you have ever seen before.\n"
"\n"
"At first you think you can take all 3, but right before you take the gun you see a few lasers protecting it and the other three pedestals. You can take one for sure, but the other two will at best be locked out of your reach or at worst be destroyed."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4137
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Take the gun!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4139
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You ready yourself before quickly snatching the gun and then running back to"
" your ship as quickly as possible. It seems you were right; the other "
"options were destroyed, but so was the rest of the ship! Thankfully, you "
"managed to escape with your prize intact. Seeing no other ship with an "
"acessible cargo bay you decide it's time to go back to your mission."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4144
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Take the drone!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4146
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You ready yourself before quickly snatching the drone and then running back "
"to your ship as quickly as possible. It seems you were right; the other "
"options were destroyed, but so was the rest of the ship! Thankfully, you "
"managed to escape with your prize intact. Seeing no other ship with an "
"acessible cargo bay you decide it's time to go back to your mission."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4151
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Take the augment!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4153
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_QUEST_WARZONE_COALITION_CEALAFORMER_RUINS_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You ready yourself before quickly snatching the augment and then running "
"back to your ship as quickly as possible. It seems you were right; the other"
" options were destroyed, but so was the rest of the ship! Thankfully, you "
"managed to escape with your prize intact. Seeing no other ship with an "
"acessible cargo bay you decide it's time to go back to your mission."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4179
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_NO_ASB\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"You've destroyed the Rebel Elite's ship: no easy task. It's not enough to "
"impact the fleet, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4182
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_NO_ASB\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4184
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_NO_ASB\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4190
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_NO_ASB\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"You've wiped out the crew of the Rebel Elite: no easy task. It's not enough "
"to impact the fleet, but it's still a great victory."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4193
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_NO_ASB\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4195
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_REBEL_NO_ASB\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Rebel ship survived the fight. Inside "
"is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4207
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_FANATIC\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You've only just arrived at the beacon when a MFK Ace ship immediately "
"rushes towards you, hailing you. \"Federation scum! You will pay for all you"
" have done to slow down humanity's progress and status! Forcing us to live "
"alongside alien scum as if we were equal! But no more! The Rebellion will "
"free us all from the chains of oppression and bring about a future fit for "
"our kind!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4210
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_FANATIC\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Have you even met any aliens before?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4212
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_FANATIC\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your words don't even register to the MFK Ace. They cut the feed and attempt"
" to attack you while your weapons are offline. Thankfully the shot misses, "
"but their message is clear: you can't avoid this fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4214
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_FANATIC\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4231
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_AUTO_NO_ASB\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4233
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_AUTO_NO_ASB\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Innovation Auto ship survived the fight. Inside is"
" a functional sentry weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4242
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_HACK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you can even react, all of your subsystems are instantly hacked, with"
" only piloting remaining barely functional. You quickly find the culprit, a "
"Innovation Saboteur who identified you as a threat and is moving in to "
"engage."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4249
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_HACK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4253
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_HACK\"]/choice[@req=\"ANTI_VIRUS\"]/text"
msgstr "(Anti-Virus) Prevent their hacking."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4255
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_HACK\"]/choice[@req=\"ANTI_VIRUS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Anti-Virus works its magic and counters the digital assault without any "
"problems."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4261
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_HACK\"]/choice[@req=\"ANTI_VIRUS\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4267
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_HACK\"]/choice[@req=\"hacking\"]/text"
msgstr "(Hacking) Prevent their hacking."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4269
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_HACK\"]/choice[@req=\"hacking\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Innovation ship's virus is much harder to purge than you expected, and "
"you have to overclock the hacking system. Your systems return to normal, but"
" your hacking has taken a huge loss."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4276
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_AUTO_HACK\"]/choice[@req=\"hacking\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4285
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"As you watch the Coalition vessel break apart, you reflect on what a stupid "
"acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4288
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4290
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4293
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4300
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"As their last crew falls, you reflect on what a stupid acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" "
"is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4303
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4305
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4308
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4317
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You, at first, find yourself alone near the unpopulated moon on this beacon."
" That is, until a R.U.E.S. ship comes out of hiding, guns blazing!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4321
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Prepare for combat!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4323
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship hails you. A Saboteur appears on screen and chuckles. \"Come on, "
"Renegade, did you really think this ship was all we had on this beacon?\" "
"The slug snickers and then grins. \"Oh nonono, in fact, I guess you can say "
"you've fallen into our little... trap.\" the slug bursts out laughing as "
"your boarder alarms blare! You also detect more teleporter signatures "
"flaring up on the nearby moon; they must be using the R.U.E.S. ship as a way"
" to track your ship's location!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4327
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//triggeredEvent[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING_WAVE_LOOP\"]/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"More elite Coalition soldiers will board your ship! End the fight with the "
"enemy ship to stop them!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4332
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4338
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_mantis_queen\"]/text"
msgstr "(Leikonpliiinakra) Have Leikonpliiinakra hail them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4340
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_mantis_queen\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Leikonpliiinakra doesn't need to even say a word before the enemy ship's "
"weapons power down. \"...sssshit...\" The Saboteur mutters before sending a "
"gun and some resouces as an apology."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4347
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/text"
msgstr "(Nights) Have Nights hail them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4349
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_nights\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Nights doesn't need to even say a word before the enemy ship's weapons power"
" down. \"...sssshit...\" The Saboteur mutters before sending a gun and some "
"resouces as an apology."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4356
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tyrdeo\"]/text"
msgstr "(Tyrdeo) Have Tyrdeo hail them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4358
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tyrdeo\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Tyrdeo doesn't need to even say a word before the enemy ship's weapons power"
" down. \"...sssshit...\" The Saboteur mutters before sending a gun and some "
"resouces as an apology."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4367
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING_WAVE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Like clockwork another wave of Coalition elites board your ship! If you want"
" to end this endless tide of death then you must dispose of the enemy ship!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4372
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As the R.U.E.S. ship finally falls, your alarms go silent and all the "
"detected teleporter signatures vanish from your sensors. You at least now "
"have the breathing room to do something aboard your ship and double check "
"where you fought the ship for any extra resouces you might have missed.."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4376
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING_WIN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4380
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_BOARDING_WIN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4388
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_NO_ASB\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"As you watch the Coalition vessel break apart, you reflect on what a stupid "
"acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4391
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_NO_ASB\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4393
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_NO_ASB\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4399
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_NO_ASB\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"As their last crew falls, you reflect on what a stupid acronym \"R.U.E.S.\" "
"is. Like seriously, who even came up with that?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4402
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_NO_ASB\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4404
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_COALITION_NO_ASB\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems that the cargo of the Elite Coalition ship survived the fight. "
"Inside is a functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4413
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_ASTEROID\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"While uncommon, there are still a few asteroid belts in this sector. The "
"Federation, Rebellion, and Coalition avoid them as places for skirmishes, as"
" it turns combat into something a lot more hectic for all parties involved. "
"Sometimes, though, individual ships still tactically use them for one-on-one"
" fights. Case in point, the R.U.E.S. ship here that's advancing towards you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4417
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_ASTEROID\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4419
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_ASTEROID\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship hails you. They seem to have an Ampere as their captain. \"God "
"dammit, I knew even the asteroid belts weren't safe! You know what? I'm "
"tired of having to avoid you renegades everytime we need to scout a beacon! "
"Time for you to finally fear our alliance!\" the leech screams before "
"powering on the ship's weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4422
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_ASTEROID\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4441
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Elite pirates have become a plague on this sector, swarming civilian and "
"defenseless ships alike and shaking them down for everything they have. Case"
" in point, the elite pirate that seems to be preying on weaker ships at this"
" beacon. The captain grins widely. \"Well well well, what do we have here? A"
" small Renegade all alone, without their nosey Federation friends around to "
"help, hm? Well, I can let you through unharmed... for a price.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4444
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "We refuse to pay the fee, fight your way through!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4446
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You mute the ship and prepare for combat. However, before you can properly "
"start the fight, the pirate activates a combat augment, heavily limiting "
"your engines!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4450
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/choice[1]/event/triggeredEvent/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr "You've been affected by an engine jammer!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4455
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4461
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/text"
msgstr "(Purple Beard) \"... No\"."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4463
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate's eyes widen before they chuckle, clearly unconfortable. \"O-of "
"course, Captain... H-Here, please have this! Think of it as an apology "
"gift!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4468
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Pay the fee."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4470
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_SHAKEDOWN\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Good choice... veeery good choice.\" The pirate captain chuckles and "
"starts counting your scrap."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4480
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"No matter how influential they were, at the end of the day they were still "
"pirates. As you watch their ill-gotten station crumble to dust, you breath a"
" sigh of relief that they won't make this sector even more of a hellish "
"place."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4483
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/destroyed/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_pirate_station_tricked\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4485
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/destroyed/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_pirate_station_tricked\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As you scrap the station's debris you find what seems to be the pirate's "
"safe. Inside it are crates containing all the resources you gave them and "
"more!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4495
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/destroyed/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_pirate_station_tricked\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4497
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/destroyed/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_pirate_station_tricked\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As you scrap the station's debris you find what seems to be the pirate's "
"safe. Inside it are crates containing a bunch of extra resources!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4507
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Not even the toughest pirates can stop you now. That's one less plague to "
"torment this sector."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4510
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/deadCrew/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_pirate_station_tricked\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4512
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/deadCrew/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_pirate_station_tricked\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As you scrap the station's rooms you find what seems to be the pirate's "
"safe. Inside of it are crates containing all the resources you gave them and"
" more!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4522
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/deadCrew/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_pirate_station_tricked\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4524
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_STATION_PIRATE_TRICK\"]/deadCrew/choice[@req=\"loc_fr_pirate_station_tricked\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As you scrap the station's rooms you find what seems to be the pirate's "
"safe. Inside it are crates containing a bunch of extra resources!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4539
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you land you are hailed by a nearby elite pirate sation. \"Oi! "
"Feddy boy! You think you can just land on *our* beacon and walk around like "
"you own the place?! Give us 50 scrap and some missiles and drone parts or we"
" might need to teach you a lesson on good manners!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4542
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attack the pirates!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4544
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"This outlaws shouldn't be allowed to stay in Federation territory with "
"stations like those! Take those bastards down!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4547
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4553
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/text"
msgstr "(Purple Beard) \"... No... We do not.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4555
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_unique_purple_beard\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The pirate's eyes widen before they take a step back, hands raised "
"defensevly. \"O-Oh... y-yes! O-Of course! P-Please, take this! Call it a "
"uh... apology gift! P-Please don't ruin my reputation... i-i don't want to "
"go back to piloting Union shuttles...\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4560
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Pay the 'fee'."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4562
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Good. See? Wasn't this so much easier than fighting?\" The pirate captain chuckles, but doesn't cut the feed. He grins and turns to his second in command to the right of him. \"Say, Joie, what if we used some of that good old pirate freedom that we have been promised when we defacted?\" You can't see the other pirate but you can hear them chuckling loudly.\n"
"\n"
"\"Sorry, little Feddy buddy, but it seems your scrap isn't enough. No, we want something a lot more valuable than that... how about your ship and crew?\" The pirate smirks and powers on their weapons! You might be able to recover your wasted goods if you kill them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4573
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_PIRATE_STATION\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4586
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"With how frantic this sector is for those enlisted in the Federation's "
"fleet, it's no wonder that sometimes mistakes are bound to happen. Case in "
"point, the Unity ship that mistook you for a rebel spy."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4589
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attempt to clear up the missunderstanding."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4591
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[1]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to convince the Unity ship of your innocence, but your words fall on"
" deaf ears. There's no avoiding this fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4594
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[1]/event[1]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4599
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[1]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You somehow say the right words to avoid a fight. The Unity ship apologises "
"and even sends some supplies to help your mission."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4605
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tully\"]/text"
msgstr "(Tully) Clear up the misunderstanding."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4607
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[@req=\"unique_tully\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The sight of Admiral Tully immediate puts the Unity captain at ease. \"Ah, "
"Admiral Tully. It's good to see you on the front lines. I'm sorry for "
"accusing you of being a Rebel; I will be more careful in the future. Please,"
" have our spare resources. We also have a skilled Engi on board that might "
"be able to give your ship some repairs as well.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4618
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Fight the ship!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4620
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"If they want a fight so bad, then it's about time you show them what happens"
" to traitors!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4623
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_MISTAKE\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4636
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"While generally relaible, it seems someone must have messed with this auto's"
" sensors, as it seems to think you are a threat!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4639
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attempt to fix the auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4641
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[1]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Without any skilled engineer aboard your ship, it's no surprise the repair "
"failed. A fight is inevitable!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4644
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[1]/event[1]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4649
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[1]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"By some miracle you manage to undo whatever error there was with its "
"sensors. The ship now sees you as an ally and gives you some goodies."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4654
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/text"
msgstr "(Engi Crew) Repair the auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4656
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGI\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Engi is used to working with Federation auto ships, so they manage to "
"fix the auto's faulty sensors in no time! The auto even gives you some extra"
" goodies now that it knows you are an ally!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4662
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/text"
msgstr "(Engineer Crew) Repair the auto."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4664
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_ENGINEER\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Engineer tries their best, but they struggle to work with the different"
" Federation standards for the auto. While attempting to reset the auto's "
"threat list, they acidentally connect the wrong wire to the wrong place, "
"causing a chain reaction that quickly destroys the auto. At least you can "
"scrap its remains..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4670
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Fight the ship!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4672
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You can't risk a Federation auto with its sensors broken continuing to be "
"loose in such a dangerous sector, it will do more harm than good."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4675
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_FEDERATION_AUTO\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4684
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS_DOUBLE\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"Even the Hive's strongest ships have their limits, and it seems the enemy "
"Bishop has finally reached theirs. With one last crack the ship explodes "
"into pieces."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4687
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS_DOUBLE\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4689
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS_DOUBLE\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Bishop ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4692
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS_DOUBLE\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4699
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS_DOUBLE\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Mantis Bishops are some of the best warriors the multiverse has to offer. "
"They capture the perfect mix of speed and power. No matter how mighty, "
"though, all warriors must fall one day."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4702
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS_DOUBLE\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4704
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS_DOUBLE\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Bishop ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4707
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_MANTIS_DOUBLE\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4722
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_DOUBLE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You catch the conversation between two ships, a Bishop and a Knight. The "
"topic at first seems to consist of their favorite holidays, with the Slug "
"prefering the Crown Theft Festival and the Mantis, Renegade Day. However, as"
" soon as they notice you, they quickly shift topics. \"Ah! Slanky! Seem we "
"have eaves dropper!\" The Bishop speaks in a threatening tone while the Slug"
" just chuckles. \"And you know what we do to eavessssdroppers right? You got"
" thissss, right Trakitep?\" the Slug chuckles again, with the Mantis nodding"
" and powering on their weapons."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4725
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_DOUBLE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4733
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG_DOUBLE\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"No matter how imposing Night's ships are, they lack the discipline and "
"training that other elites tend to get. Their dirty tactics clearly failed "
"them today as their ship breaks apart at the seams."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4736
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG_DOUBLE\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4738
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG_DOUBLE\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Knight ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4741
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG_DOUBLE\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4748
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG_DOUBLE\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Knight crew are extremely resilient and are equipped with the best tech the "
"Kleptocracy has to offer. Still, they die like any others."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4751
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG_DOUBLE\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4753
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG_DOUBLE\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Knight ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4756
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_SELITE_SLUG_DOUBLE\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4770
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_DOUBLE_MANTIS_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Knight looks devastated. They blink for a few moments before gritting "
"their teeth and powering on their weapons. \"You.... you... YOU PIECE OF "
"CRAP RENEGADE! I WILL TEAR YOU APART FOR WHAT YOU DID TO MY FRIEND!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4773
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_DOUBLE_MANTIS_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4779
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_COALITION_DOUBLE_SLUG_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"With the Knight out of the way, you are free to do a full search of the "
"battlefield. You find what seems to be the map for the sector as well the "
"flight plans for the Coalition in this sector. Maybe you can delay the "
"rebels by forcing them to follow you through heavily reinforced Coalition "
"routes?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4787
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER_AUTO\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The automated Technician ship has been destroyed. Hopefully not too many "
"lives were lost keeping it at bay before you arrived."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4790
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER_AUTO\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4792
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER_AUTO\"]/destroyed/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems the cargo of the Technician ship survived the fight. Inside is a "
"functional weapon, which you bring back on board."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4795
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_ELITE_ENGINEER_AUTO\"]/destroyed/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4805
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN_AUTO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you land you are immediately confronted by a Technician ship, "
"weapons hot. However, when it hails you, you don't see anyone on the other "
"side. Instead, a robotic voice speaks in a monotone and un-emotional manner."
" \"FEDERATION. THREAT. ELIMINATE.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4808
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN_AUTO\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4810
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN_AUTO\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Suddenly, you are hailed by a small Technician shuttle, with a pair of twins"
" on the other side. \"Renegade! I never thought we would be happy to see one"
" of you around! We were trying to install kind of base automation system on "
"our ship but we acidentally made it go haywire! It killed most of our crew "
"because it sees everyone as a threat! It destroyed our support auto and "
"almost obliterated our escort MFK Ace ship! Please, don't let it kill anyone"
" else!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4812
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN_AUTO\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4820
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_HOSTILE_WARZONE_REBEL_TECHNICIAN_AUTO_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The shuttle hails you \"Man... it will suck having to explain what happened "
"to our boss... But I suppose you did save us from a lot more trouble if that"
" thing had gone unchallenged. Thank you! We don't have much on us, but we "
"can give the fleet some, let's say, 'outdated' information on your "
"whereabouts as a thank you. How does that sound?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4857
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The strange ship crumples before your very eyes, its hull tearing apart "
"before something deep within the ship explodes, completely destroying "
"everything around the ship, including any loot. At least your scrap returns "
"are plentiful."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4861
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Before the last soldier falls, they send out one last encrypted command to their ship's systems. Your crew quickly evacuates, thinking it was a self destruct command, but nothing happens. \n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"Once you feel safe enough to return and explore the ship, you realize what the command did: it wiped out every single storage system in the ship completely clean. Seems like this mystery will live on for now."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4866
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4868
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"At least it seems that their cargo survived the fight. You find the most "
"expensive looking weapon and bring it back onboard."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4876
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you finish your jump, you are met with a strange ship waiting for you. "
"Their colors don't ring any bells and your database doesn't even return a "
"name for whoever they represent. What you can tell for sure though is that "
"they don't seem friendly at all: their weapons are already powering up!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4879
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4881
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before a fight actually starts, your ship detects a signal being emitted "
"from the ship. However, it's encrypted so heavily that it would take months "
"for your ship to even have a chance to decypher what they just sent."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4883
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_human_totality\"]/text"
msgstr "(Totality Commander) Decrypt the signal."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4885
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_human_totality\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your commander is hesitant at first, but soon agrees to help you. However, they refuse to decrypt the message to you, only telling you what the message was about. It seems this is an Assault vessel built specifically to track rogue Renegades like you. After a lot of persuasion, they agree to ask for the other vessel back down from the fight.\n"
"\n"
"\"Bird of Prey, this is Nested Owl. The Eagle is hunting its own. I repeat, the Eagle is hunting its own. Over.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4889
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_human_totality\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4891
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_human_totality\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"After what feels like hours, the enemy ship's weapons power down. Another "
"message is sent, but like before, your commander refuses to share it with "
"you. All they say is that this specific ship will back down from hunting "
"you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4895
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_human_totality\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4899
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_human_totality\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4907
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Fight the ship!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4909
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You have no idea what this ship wants, but if it's a fight they are after, "
"it's one they will get."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml:4911
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_warzone.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_FINISH_BEACON_WARZONE_TOTALITY\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."
